Quiz Schema:
    {
        "title": "string",
        "questions": [
            {
                "question": "string",
                "options": {
                    "1": "option1",
                    "2": "option2",
                    ...
                },
                "ansewerOption": "integer"
            }
        ],
        "createdAt": "time",
        "updatedAt": "time"
    }

Routes:
    1. POST /api/quiz
        create quiz route. will be authorized route(middleware will be added after implementing authentication)

    2. UPDATE /api/quiz/:id 
        update quiz title, questions and correct option(will be authorized too)

    3. DELETE /api/quiz/:id
        delete quiz(authorized)